  "title": "Wall of Fame",
  "heading": "Manitoba Fiddle Association - Wall of Fame",
  "bodyHtml": "\n\t<h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"text-align:left;\">Manitoba Fiddle Association - Wall of Fame</h2>\n\n<div class=\"paragraph\">The Wall of Fame is an initiative of the Manitoba Fiddle Association.<br>Through artistic display, text and visual exhibits, it is a place where:<ul><li><span>﻿</span>the public can learn about fiddle music and its history</li><li>historical artifacts from Manitoba's fiddle history can be exhibited</li><li>many talented Manitoba fiddlers and friends of the fiddle can be recognized</li></ul></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\"><div style=\"height: 10px; overflow: hidden;\"></div>\n<a class=\"wsite-button wsite-button-small wsite-button-highlight\" href=\"/inductee-history.html\">\n<span class=\"wsite-button-inner\">Inductee History</span>\n</a>\n<div style=\"height: 10px; overflow: hidden;\"></div></div>\n\n<div><div style=\"height: 20px; overflow: hidden; width: 100%;\"></div>\n<hr class=\"styled-hr\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n<div style=\"height: 20px; overflow: hidden; width: 100%;\"></div></div>\n\n<div><div class=\"wsite-multicol\"><div class=\"wsite-multicol-table-wrap\" style=\"margin:0 -15px;\">\n\t<table class=\"wsite-multicol-table\">\n\t\t<tbody class=\"wsite-multicol-tbody\">\n\t\t\t<tr class=\"wsite-multicol-tr\">\n\t\t\t\t<td class=\"wsite-multicol-col\" style=\"width:33.333333333333%; padding:0 15px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n<h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\">Fiddler-Performer Category<br><span></span></h2>\n\n<div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align:left;\">Those individuals who have brought fame to the province and&nbsp;themselves through their outstanding fiddle music and works.<br><span></span></div>\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t</td>\t\t\t\t<td class=\"wsite-multicol-col\" style=\"width:33.333333333333%; padding:0 15px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n<h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"text-align:left;\">Builder-Promoter Category<br><span></span></h2>\n\n<div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align:left;\">Those individuals who have given extensively of their time and&nbsp;talent in the development and promotion of fiddle music in their&nbsp;community.</div>\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t</td>\t\t\t\t<td class=\"wsite-multicol-col\" style=\"width:33.333333333333%; padding:0 15px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n<h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"text-align:left;\">Accompanist Category<br><span></span></h2>\n\n<div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align:left;\">Those individuals who have given extensively of their musical talent&nbsp;to accent fiddlers' music.<br><span></span></div>\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t</td>\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t</tbody>\n\t</table>\n</div></div></div>\n\n<div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align:left;\">Induction includes a plaque bearing the person's photograph and biography.<br><span></span></div>\n\n<div><div style=\"height: 20px; overflow: hidden; width: 100%;\"></div>\n<hr class=\"styled-hr\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n<div style=\"height: 20px; overflow: hidden; width: 100%;\"></div></div>\n\n<div><div class=\"wsite-multicol\"><div class=\"wsite-multicol-table-wrap\" style=\"margin:0 -15px;\">\n\t<table class=\"wsite-multicol-table\">\n\t\t<tbody class=\"wsite-multicol-tbody\">\n\t\t\t<tr class=\"wsite-multicol-tr\">\n\t\t\t\t<td class=\"wsite-multicol-col\" style=\"width:50%; padding:0 15px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n<div class=\"wsite-map\"><iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 250px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\" src=\"//www.weebly.com/weebly/apps/generateMap.php?map=google&amp;elementid=150832413762649573&amp;ineditor=0&amp;control=3&amp;width=auto&amp;height=250px&amp;overviewmap=0&amp;scalecontrol=0&amp;typecontrol=0&amp;zoom=15&amp;long=-98.00439360000001&amp;lat=49.5094388&amp;domain=www&amp;point=1&amp;align=2&amp;reseller=true\"></iframe></div>\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t</td>\t\t\t\t<td class=\"wsite-multicol-col\" style=\"width:50%; padding:0 15px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n<div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><font size=\"3\">The Wall of Fame is located at:<br><span></span>  Carman Community Hall<br><span></span>  60 1st Avenue NW<br><span></span>  Carman, MB</font><br><span></span></div>\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t</td>\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t</tbody>\n\t</table>\n</div></div></div>\n",
